description:
A psychology student forming the two-person occult circle, the Secret Seals Club, along with Usami Renko. She is a descendant of a long line of magicians with the ability to see boundaries, and while she is an inhabitant of the Outside World, thanks to her ability she has already crossed the boundaries of the Gensokyo.
She is not used to her ability and she sometimes has difficulties telling the difference between dream and reality, and she tends to put herself in dangerous situations because of that.
name: Maribel Hearn
